{"id":144683,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/《译者》每日推荐-2011414/","date":"2011-04-15T04:01:06Z","modified":"2011-04-15T04:01:06Z","title":"《译者》每日推荐 &#8211; 2011/4/14","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【热点评论】</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span>– <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/artanddesign/jonathanjonesblog/2011/apr/14/ai-weiwei-china-human-rights\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">是中国在受审判，而不是艾未未</span></a></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span>– <a href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/18561005\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">太子党和警察国家</span></a></p>\n<p>CNN – <a href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/asiapcf/04/13/china.dissident.arrests/index.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">又有一位中国异议人士被捕</span></a></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span>– <a href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/14/us-china-usa-cyberespionage-idUSTRE73D24220110414\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">网络谍对谍，中国占优势</span></a></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span>– <a href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/indian-decade/2011/04/14/why-brics-2011-is-important/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">金砖五国的意义</span></a></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span>– <a href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/china_other_developing_brics_nations_seek_change_in_global_economic_order/2011/04/14/AFarMgdD_story.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国和其他金砖国家寻求改变世界经济秩序</span></a></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【社会百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">绿色和平组织</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span>– <a href=\"http://www.greenpeace.org/raw/content/eastasia/press/reports/coal-ash-dust-storm.pdf\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的沙尘暴实际上是有毒物质</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（</span>PDF<s